{"tid":2097554,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"7-11曾經賣千層肉醬？","createTime":"2020-07-07T02:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T02:21:20.000Z","uid":69460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f84c2cc95018ec786f85d885bd4f1fb02872da8","tid":2097554,"uid":69460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"有無人記得 2005年左右香港7-11曾經賣過千層肉醬有好多紅定黑豆裏面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時賣成廿幾蚊但好厚料幾飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔似千層蛋糕咁瘋魔絕版又再出返<br />\n雲呢拿可樂 Qoo橙汁有途徑搵得返<br />\n呢個千層肉醬完全消失咗唔知係咪以微波爐食物黎講製作成本高<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人知係咩牌子而家完全搵唔返任何資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}